text.english: He also destroyed all the firstborn in their land, The first of all their strength. Egypt was glad when they departed, For the fear of them had fallen upon them.
text.arabic: قَتَلَ كُلَّ بِكْرٍ فِي أَرْضِهِمْ أَوَائِلَ كُلِّ قُوَّتِهِمْ. فَرِحَتْ مِصْرُ بِخُرُوجِهِمْ لأَنَّ رُعْبَهُمْ سَقَطَ عَلَيْهِمْ.
